terraform expressions

- helps us to avoid the rewriting the code again and again.

- similar to function as we can reuse the code

there different terraform expressions we have;

conditional expressions - considers true or false

dynamic blocks - helps us to write nested block with multiple values

splat expressions - help us to retrieve multiple values using single line with * operator

